# mmo: the clickening

## installing

1. Install [meteor](https://www.meteor.com/): `$ curl https://install.meteor.com/ | sh`
2. Create a new project: `$ meteor create tmp`
3. Clone this repository: `$ git clone https://github.com/Thimoteus/mmo-the-clickening`
4. Move meteor files into repository directory: `$ mv tmp/* mmo-the-clickening/ && rmdir tmp`
5. Change directories: `$ cd mmo-the-clickening`
6. Install dependencies: `$ meteor add coffeescript less accounts-ui accounts-facebook`
7. Run the server: `$ meteor`
8. Go to `localhost:3000` on your browser!